title: Feds increase oversight of Ohio marketplace co-op (HPIO - Health Policy Institute of Ohio)
text: ( Source : HPIO - Health Policy Institute of Ohio ) The federal government is increasing its scrutiny of an Ohio cooperative that was set up to help ensure a lower-cost option for Ohioans who shop the federally run health-insurance marketplace
